Nigeria sensational musician and popular RnB singer, Sound Sultan has announced the release date for his 8th studio album titled ‘8th Wonder’ on which he is set to feature seven other Nigerian musicians. The Natural Something crooner, who took to his twitter handle to announce the release date of the new album, has revealed that the album would drop on 27th of March and it will feature artistes such as Wizkid, 2face, Falz, Small Doctor, Perruzi, Johne Drille and Abiola. The star studded album is coming from the Naija Ninja boss four years after he released his seventh album ‘Out of the Box’ in 2016, on which he also featured 2face idibia, Patoranking and Sarkodie. SHOCKING LIFE STORY!!! Abuja Man reveals (FREE) secret Fruits that Increased his Manh0d size and Lasting Power in just 7days… CLICK HERE TO GET IT!!!